-You're welcome.

182
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,790
You humans would help each other.

183
00:11:18,020 --> 00:11:19,370
Demons would do that too.

184
00:11:19,950 --> 00:11:21,130
Although I'm young,

185
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,370
I understand

186
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:23,370
