227
00:13:27,070 --> 00:13:28,670
How could we abandon her

228
00:13:28,670 --> 00:13:29,750
just because she's a demon?

229
00:13:30,790 --> 00:13:31,680
A demon

230
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:34,440
